title: Daily Review with Clay and Buck - Apr 26 2022
itunes:title: Daily Review with Clay and Buck - Apr 26 2022
description:
Why Elon Musk Buying Twitter Is Such A Big Deal - and The left is freaking out about Elon Musk buying Twitter, as heard in sound bites featuring hosts from CNN & MSNBC. A Federal judge in Louisiana has temporarily blocked the Biden administration from ending the Title 42 restriction. NY Post writer Miranda Devine on the latest news on Hunter Biden's laptop- and the impact of Elon Musk buying Twitter - and what it means for the New York Post - and free speech. Author Douglas Murray talks about how the War on the West has been going on for several years.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
